<item>Slowly peel off the two pieces by pulling on the handle of the bottom piece.</item>
<item>Gently stroke your finger along the top of the second piece of tape (i.e., the nonsticky side), as shown in <link target-id="Figure_18_01_scotchb_img"/>(b).</item>
<item>Peel the two pieces of tape apart by pulling on their handles, as shown in <link target-id="Figure_18_01_scotchb_img"/>(c).</item>
