<para id="fs-id1164565949354">You have four neutral conducting spheres and a charging device that allows you to place charge <emphasis effect="italics">q</emphasis> on any neutral object. You want to charge one sphere with a charge <emphasis effect="italics">q</emphasis>/2 and the other three with a charge <emphasis effect="italics">q</emphasis>6 . How do you proceed?</para>
